items.title: Awesome Openstreetmap
items.content_text:
### Editors / Mobile Editors

*   [GoMap!!](http://gomaposm.com) - Feature-rich mobile editor for iOS. ([iOS](https://apps.apple.com/app/id592990211) / [Source Code (⭐362)](https://github.com/bryceco/GoMap) / [Wiki](https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Go_Map!!))
*   [Every Door](https://every-door.app) - Every Door is an Android and iOS app that lets you create and edit objects in OpenStreetMap. It supports editing node and polygon features, and creating point features like shops, benches, and building entrances. ([Android](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=info.zverev.ilya.every_door) / [iOS](https://apps.apple.com/app/id1621945342) / [Source Code (⭐468)](https://github.com/zverik/every_door) / [Wiki](https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Every_Door))
items.content_html:
Editors / Mobile Editors

  • GoMap!! - Feature-rich mobile editor for iOS. (iOS / Source Code (⭐362) / Wiki)
  • Every Door - Every Door is an Android and iOS app that lets you create and edit objects in OpenStreetMap. It supports editing node and polygon features, and creating point features like shops, benches, and building entrances. (Android / iOS / Source Code (⭐468) / Wiki)
